transform_def.name: designed_3rd04
transform_def.string: let r = 1 / length(p_in) r1 = 2 / length(p_in) r2 = 0.5 / length(p_in) a1 = sin(abs(sin(p_in.x)) - abs(sin(p_in.y))) a2 = cos(abs(cos(p_in.x)) - abs(cos(p_in.y))) a = fmod(a1, a2) / tanh(p_in.x) b1 = sin(abs(sin(p_in.x)) + abs(sin(p_in.y))) b2 = cos(abs(cos(p_in.x)) + abs(cos(p_in.y))) b = fmod(b1, b2) / tanh(p_in.y) z = fmod(a, b) / tanh(p_in.x * p_in.y) con0 = abs(z) > r1 con1 = abs(z) < r1 && abs(z) > r2 con2 = abs(z) < r2 in (if if fill <= 0.0 then con0 else if fill > 0.25 then con2 else con1 then p_in else vec2(0.0)) * weight
